d's 'The Lovely Bones'</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">May 28, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/pollystewart/">Polly Stewart</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/paula-bomer-stalker-essay/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/05/stalker-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/paula-bomer-stalker-essay/">Because He Can: Paula Bomer on Capturing Entitlement and the Banality of Sociopathy</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">May 28, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/paulabomer/">Paula Bomer</a></span></div></li><li><div class="post_circle_thumb"><a href="https://crimereads.com/7-historical-novels-that-explore-the-underbelly-of-the-art-world/"><img class="lazy" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/plugins/lb-content-widgets/img/lazy-sq.png" data-src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2025/05/art-world-theft-feat-150x150.jpg" alt=""></a></div><div class="text-container"><strong class="title"><a href="https://crimereads.com/7-historical-novels-that-explore-the-underbelly-of-the-art-world/">7 Historical Novels That Explore The Underbelly of the Art World</a></strong><span class="post_attribute center"><span class="post_detail_date">May 27, 2025</span> by <a href="https://crimereads.com/author/lauraleffler/">Laura Leffler</a></span></div></li></ul></li>
